{"tid":2147710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美軍來了，解放軍匿係無人島打飛機","createTime":"2020-08-09T12:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T12:12:35.000Z","uid":265313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19ab6b200e874d42eaf950afbaca1eb01f0f3c18","tid":2147710,"uid":265313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T12:12:35.000Z","msg":"笑死，平時吹到一小時武統台灣，宜家美軍真的來了，成班去咗無人島打飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20200809/s00004/1596961435078/%e7%be%8e%e8%a1%9b%e7%94%9f%e9%83%a8%e9%95%b7%e8%a8%aa%e5%8f%b0%e5%89%8d%e5%a4%95-%e8%a7%a3%e6%94%be%e8%bb%8d%e5%8d%97%e6%b5%b7%e6%bc%94%e7%bf%92%e6%90%b6%e7%81%98%e7%99%bb%e9%99%b8-%e7%be%8e%e8%88%aa%e6%af%8d%e5%b7%a1%e9%82%8f%e6%a9%9f%e7%8f%be%e8%ba%ab%e5%8f%b0%e6%b5%b7%e3%80%90%e7%9f%ad%e7%89%87%e3%80%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20200809%2Fs00004%2F1596961435078%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%25a1%259b%25e7%2594%259f%25e9%2583%25a8%25e9%2595%25b7%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e5%258f%25b0%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%25a4%2595-%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e6%2594%25be%25e8%25bb%258d%25e5%258d%2597%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e6%25bc%2594%25e7%25bf%2592%25e6%2590%25b6%25e7%2581%2598%25e7%2599%25bb%25e9%2599%25b8-%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%2588%25aa%25e6%25af%258d%25e5%25b7%25a1%25e9%2582%258f%25e6%25a9%259f%25e7%258f%25be%25e8%25ba%25ab%25e5%258f%25b0%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%259f%25ad%25e7%2589%2587%25e3%2580%2591&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=644481fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20200809%2Fs00004%2F1596961435078%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%25a1%259b%25e7%2594%259f%25e9%2583%25a8%25e9%2595%25b7%25e8%25a8%25aa%25e5%258f%25b0%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%25a4%2595-%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e6%2594%25be%25e8%25bb%258d%25e5%258d%2597%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e6%25bc%2594%25e7%25bf%2592%25e6%2590%25b6%25e7%2581%2598%25e7%2599%25bb%25e9%2599%25b8-%25e7%25be%258e%25e8%2588%25aa%25e6%25af%258d%25e5%25b7%25a1%25e9%2582%258f%25e6%25a9%259f%25e7%258f%25be%25e8%25ba%25ab%25e5%258f%25b0%25e6%25b5%25b7%25e3%2580%2590%25e7%259f%25ad%25e7%2589%2587%25e3%2580%2591&h=ee822df9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20200809/s00004/1596961435078/%e7%be%8e%e8%a1%9b%e7%94%9f%e9%83%a8%e9%95%b7%e8%a8%aa%e5%8f%b0%e5%89%8d%e5%a4%95-%e8%a7%a3%e6%94%be%e8%bb%8d%e5%8d%97%e6%b5%b7%e6%bc%94%e7%bf%92%e6%90%b6%e7%81%98%e7%99%bb%e9%99%b8-%e7%be%8e%e8%88%aa%e6%af%8d%e5%b7%a1%e9%82%8f%e6%a9%9f%e7%8f%be%e8%ba%ab%e5%8f%b0%e6%b5%b7%e3%80%90%e7%9f%ad%e7%89%87%e3%80%91</a><br />\n<br />\n美衛生部長訪台前夕 解放軍南海演習搶灘登陸 美航母巡邏機現身台海【短片】 (17:20)<br />\n<br />\n美國衛生及公共服務部長阿扎（Alex Azar）將於今日（9日）下午率團訪問台灣，成為1979年以來訪台層級最高美國內閣官員。內地官媒在阿扎訪台前刊發影片透露，解放軍第七十四集團軍近日在南海進行海上搶灘登陸演習，影片最後的解說並指出，「中國解放軍<span class=\"red\">有信心</span>有能力保衛國家主權與安全利益」。<br />\n<br />\n第七十四集團軍現駐地在廣東惠州。影片顯示，在傍晚時分，瓊西某海域擔任紅方突擊任務的第七十四集團軍某旅，分批次搭載登陸艇進行夜間航渡；至次日凌晨抵達前沿陣地。先遣部隊迅速出發，乘坐快艇開始搶灘登陸；登陸之初遭遇敵方打擊，先遣部隊遂緊急請求火力支援；火炮陣地迅速對目標地域進行飽和式打擊；登陸部隊發起聯合搶灘登陸，<span class=\"red\">最終奪佔岸灘</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另據「南海戰略態勢感知計劃」平台今日發布消息，臨近阿扎訪台之際，美國海軍「列根號」航母戰鬥群昨日（8日）現身東海展開行動。同日，美國海軍一架P-8A反潛巡邏機亦現身台灣南部海域，向西北方向朝着中國大陸海岸飛行，一度飛行至距離中國大陸海岸67.19海里（約124.4公里）的位置後折返。<br />\n（央視/解放軍報/環球網）"}]}